# GlucoGuide: Frontend UI and Data Flow Overview

This document provides a comprehensive map of the GlucoGuide application's user interface, navigation flow, and data architecture.

## 1. Frontend UI Overview

### Application Entry and Authentication
The app starts with a splash screen and proceeds to authentication if the user is not logged in.

- **[SplashScreen](file:///c:/Users/user/gg_flutter/lib/screens/splash_screen.dart)**: Initial loading screen with brand identity.
- **[LoginScreen](file:///c:/Users/user/gg_flutter/lib/screens/login_screen.dart)**: User authentication (Email/Password).
- **[SignupScreen](file:///c:/Users/user/gg_flutter/lib/screens/signup_screen.dart)**: New user registration.
- **[PreferencesScreen](file:///c:/Users/user/gg_flutter/lib/screens/preferences_screen.dart)**: Initial onboarding questionnaire for medical history and dietary choices.

### Core Experience (Post-Login)
Once authenticated, the user interacts with the dashboard and specialized feature screens.

- **[HomeScreen](file:///c:/Users/user/gg_flutter/lib/screens/home_screen.dart)**: The central hub featuring daily reminders, quick access to diet plans, and spike predictions.
- **[UserDashboardScreen](file:///c:/Users/user/gg_flutter/lib/screens/user_dashboard_screen.dart)**: Displays personal details, medical metrics (BMI, HbA1c), and profile management.

### Specialized Health Features
- **[DietPlanScreen](file:///c:/Users/user/gg_flutter/lib/screens/diet_plan_screen.dart)**: Daily meal suggestions and nutritional targets based on glycemic load.
- **[LogMealScreen](file:///c:/Users/user/gg_flutter/lib/screens/log_meal_screen.dart)**: Interface to record actual food consumption.
- **[SpikePredictionScreen](file:///c:/Users/user/gg_flutter/lib/screens/spike_prediction_screen.dart)**: Visualizes potential glucose spikes based on planned meals.
- **[ComplicationsScreen](file:///c:/Users/user/gg_flutter/lib/screens/complications_screen.dart)**: Educational and risk assessment dashboard for diabetic complications (Nephropathy, Neuropathy, etc.).
- **[SymptomCheckScreen](file:///c:/Users/user/gg_flutter/lib/screens/symptom_check_screen.dart)**: Interactive questionnaire to track and assess physical symptoms.
- **[StatsScreen](file:///c:/Users/user/gg_flutter/lib/screens/stats_screen.dart)**: Detailed historical data visualization for glucose levels and other metrics.

---

## 2. Navigation Flow

```mermaid
graph TD
    Splash[Splash Screen] --> Login[Login Screen]
    Login --> Signup[Signup Screen]
    Login --> Home[Home Screen]
    Signup --> Prefs[Preferences Screen]
    Prefs --> Home
    
    Home <--> Dashboard[User Dashboard]
    Home <--> Diet[Diet Plan]
    Home <--> Spike[Spike Prediction]
    Home <--> Stats[Stats]
    Home <--> Comp[Complications]
    
    Diet --> Log[Log Meal]
    Comp --> Symptoms[Symptom Check]
```

